We would like the ability to create release notes based on multiple 'versions' rather than just one for a project.

We add an entry for each build we make and eventually one of these builds becomes the release.  The release notes encompass all resolved issues since the last release which encompasses many builds. (and thus many versions)

Creating release notes for each version and compiling them into one master list is tedious and somewhat time-consuming.

